{"tid":788093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上報！ 連登絲打瞞男友去O camp 玩到打車輪搞到分手","createTime":"2018-08-21T08:08:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T23:38:05.000Z","uid":72009,"like":40,"dislike":278,"uniUserReply":111,"replies":[{"pid":"5a936cfee8175add038f8718e7742da7588e6127","tid":788093,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T08:08:36.000Z","msg":"日前就有一位網民於討論區「 LIHKG 討論區」發帖，指升讀大學後男友一直不準自己參與 O camp ，不過她一直很想玩，於是瞞著對方私下參與一個兩日一夜的 O camp ，她坦言過去都知道大學的「 O camp 玩得癲」，所以早有心理準備。<br />\n<br />\n到了晚上，發帖者於玩「房 Game 」時輸了，被罰與另一名男生「打車輪」，因為擔心拒絕會被其他人杯葛，於是與對方「錫錫」 30 秒，期間這位男生更數度觸摸發帖者的胸部，但她沒有反抗。<br />\n<br />\n後來這位男生又私下約她看電影，最終被男友撞破，對方直斥她是「臭雞」，又表示要分手，令發帖者非常擔心，表明不想與男友分開。<br />\n<br />\n帖民引起網民熱烈討論，不少人都狠批發帖者的行為過份，不但瞞著男友參加 O camp ，更與其他男子有親密接觸。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.sina.com.hk/news/article/20180821/1/67/1/玩出禍-瞞男友玩-O-camp-出事-港女與男同學錫錫兼摸胸-9148699.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20180821%2F1%2F67%2F1%2F%E7%8E%A9%E5%87%BA%E7%A6%8D-%E7%9E%9E%E7%94%B7%E5%8F%8B%E7%8E%A9-O-camp-%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%8B-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A5%B3%E8%88%87%E7%94%B7%E5%90%8C%E5%AD%B8%E9%8C%AB%E9%8C%AB%E5%85%BC%E6%91%B8%E8%83%B8-9148699.html&d=uDtCgsR86EXX3RESjWIgBmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=9d1789aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.sina.com.hk/news/article/20180821/1/67/1/玩出禍-瞞男友玩-O-camp-出事-港女與男同學錫錫兼摸胸-9148699.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25c7b0dc3b71bd0daace114a1ec23c20526689f3","tid":788093,"uid":195030,"like":1171,"dislike":4,"score":1167,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T08:11:32.000Z","msg":"假膠都有得上報cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"917c86b90251bbc5eb5ed1be551a6f0b5b8bb6c3","tid":788093,"uid":123920,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T08:12:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img s